message.content: DESCRIPTION: A spacious, well-organized walk-in closet or dressing room. Light wood cabinetry and shelving lines all three walls, with hanging rods holding shirts, jackets, and dresses sorted by type. In the center of the back wall is a tall unit featuring cubbyholes for shoes and drawers beneath. Woven baskets and vintage-style trunks sit atop the cabinets for extra storage. A padded bench with wooden legs is centered on a patterned area rug. To the right, a countertop with a sink and vanity mirror is partially visible; framed artwork hangs on the adjacent wall. The room is softly lit from above and painted in warm, neutral tones.
